channel.title: What the hell is up with this error?
channel.description:
When I try to load either the DLed Mopar or webclient, i get the error:
[B] Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading runescape. [/B]
To fix this try the following (in order):
1: Try closing ALL open web-browsers. 2:Try clearing your webbrowser
etc.
I have tried all of the above. what's wrong?

item.title: What the hell is up with this error?
item.dc:creator: @PatScape PatScape
item.description:
@PatScape wrote:

Nope, I finally figured it out. The client was looking for a login picture called mopar.jpg, and I had saved the pic as mopr.jpg. Simple. Thank you though, for being the only one to respond. Don’t lock this post since the answer was found though, might help others :s
